The 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

experiment
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is assigning a ball to a cell with replacement of cells available.
 There are 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$n^n$
\end_layout

\end_inset

 different ways to assign the 
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$n$
\end_layout

\end_inset

